      "Text": "Security update for python-pdm",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for python-pdm fixes the following issues:\n\nChanges in python-pdm:\n\n- CVE-2026-47763: Do not follow symlinks when writing config files (bsc#1268384)\n- CVE-2026-47763: Do not write to paths outside the scheme dir (bsc#1268385)\n- CVE-2026-47781: Update plugin installation path to use project_plugins_dir (bsc#1268386)\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
